OL,3,CPoet-ree trail for Birmingham poet
OL,4,CBenjamin Zephaniah
OL,6,FITV Central reporter Ravneet Nandra
OL,7,Fspoke to family members and friends of
OL,8,Fthe late Benjamin Zephaniah
OL,10,FThe life of Birmingham poet, musician
OL,11,Fand actor Benjamin Zephaniah has been
OL,12,Fcelebrated in a new tree trail near
OL,13,Fhis home.
OL,15,F65 trees have been planted in Burbury
OL,16,FPark with 65 poems attached to them to
OL,17,Fcreate a poet-ree trail, to remember
OL,18,Fhis love of poems and nature.
