OL,3,CPoet-ree trail for Birmingham poet
OL,4,CBenjamin Zephaniah
OL,6,FThe first tree was planted by his wife
OL,7,FQian Zephaniah, through to the final
OL,8,F65th tree planted by his family,
OL,9,Ffriends, community, and poets.
OL,11,FBenjamin and his family lived on Farm
OL,12,FStreet when he was a child, just
OL,13,Fopposite Burbury park, so it was a
OL,14,Fchance for the community to follow in
OL,15,Fhis footsteps.
OL,17,FBenjamin died in December 2023 aged
OL,18,F65, after being diagnosed with a brain
OL,19,Ftumour.
