OL,3,CPoet-ree trail for Birmingham poet
OL,4,CBenjamin Zephaniah
OL,6,FAs well as the trees, Birmingham
OL,7,FTreePeople and the Benjamin Zephaniah
OL,8,FLegacy Group worked together to find
OL,9,Fpoets to submit their own poems in a
OL,10,Fcompetition.
OL,12,FThe theme had to be connected to
OL,13,Fnature and Benjamin's legacy as not
OL,14,Fonly a poet, but an actor and activist.
OL,16,FKeith Bracey, or 'The Birmingham
OL,17,FBard,' was successful in the
OL,18,Fcompetition and wrote the poem
OL,19,F'Benjamin Zephaniah-The Elevated Soul.'
