OL,3,CPoet-ree trail for Birmingham poet
OL,4,CBenjamin Zephaniah
OL,6,F"He was above all men because he
OL,7,Fwasn't just a poet. He was an
OL,8,Factivist. He was an actor. I mentioned
OL,9,FPeaky Blinders at the end because he
OL,10,Fwas Jeremiah Jesus. And looking over
OL,11,Fthe Garrison at the end of the poem."
OL,13,FCommunications officer for Birmingham
OL,14,FTreePeople, Charlotte McDermott made
OL,15,Fsure a variety of trees were planted,
OL,16,Ffrom fig, to maple trees, to help
OL,17,Fincrease the biodiversity in the park.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
