OL,3,CPoet-ree trail for Birmingham poet
OL,4,CBenjamin Zephaniah
OL,6,F"It's worth doing the trial just to
OL,7,Fsee the amount of species that we've
OL,8,Fput into this park. And the point is,
OL,9,Fwe want to help bio diversify our
OL,10,Fclimate, and we want to have, you
OL,11,Fknow, climate-proof our parks, make
OL,12,Fsure we don't lose any more."
OL,14,FThe poems have been laminated and tied
OL,15,Fto the trees to prevent disturbing or
OL,16,Fdamaging them.
